msgid ""
"Type of the returned array and of the accumulator in which the elements are "
"summed.  If `dtype` is not specified, it defaults to the dtype of `a`, "
"unless `a` has an integer dtype with a precision less than that of the "
"default platform integer.  In that case, the default platform integer is "
"used."
msgstr ""

